{"tid":981931,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話卡通界越嚟越多賣肉作，有冇數據證明下呀？","createTime":"2019-01-14T16:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T07:13:05.000Z","uid":105678,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5bcd58d7e055ee3388d815be859dd2d242ee86","tid":981931,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"明明依加啲卡通一季比一季好睇，種類多元化、市埸受眾又廣<br />\n<br />\n班毒撚就日日係度屌現代卡通賣肉乜乜柒柒，同啲老嘢話後生係廢青一樣心態，總之自己個時代乜都好，後來者都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n做卡通毒撚都可以做到咁老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86bb883b338432adaccf19c99772fc7a69cabb84","tid":981931,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一 最牛逼之作<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36590bd393c28dede545fe95886e94520fb7de9b","tid":981931,"uid":79077,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a178977095f84fedbedc8f74948960664a5c32e","tid":981931,"uid":125203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36590bd393c28dede545fe95886e94520fb7de9b","tid":981931,"uid":79077,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5e36bdeb90d5567fffaaff7f46d4b9b7b6201a","tid":981931,"uid":189937,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"我都覺班老閪好撚麻煩 講到以前無賣肉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係以前 2015年個四天王會TV化到？<br />\n如果係以前 賢者之孫 手機俠呢啲神作又可以TV化到？<br />\n如果係以前 落第同學戰都市可以同一季播出泥？<br />\n事實就係以前個年代不斷埋沒神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加個啲不知幾好睇<br />\n利申 醉愛刀劍"},{"pid":"cdb36d181cc4f99dfddb4157cc22eabb8e97204d","tid":981931,"uid":105678,"like":0,"disli